    {
        "sha": "f605f0b68d683debccbe7cee1968ece2fb9ab5ec",
        "author": "Roy Arsan",
        "email": "royarsan@anthropic.com",
        "date": "2026-06-29T23:02:43Z",
        "message": "Gateway GCP example: Agent Platform rebrand and README cleanup\n\n- Update Vertex AI prose references to Agent Platform across the example\n  (READMEs, script/terraform comments, config template). Functional\n  identifiers are unchanged: the 'provider: vertex' config key,\n  roles/aiplatform.user, aiplatform.googleapis.com, and the terraform\n  resource label (renaming it would recreate the IAM binding in existing\n  states). First mentions keep '(formerly Vertex AI)' for searchability.\n- Drop the README's self-referential public-mirror link.",
        "url": "https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code/commit/f605f0b68d683debccbe7cee1968ece2fb9ab5ec"
    },
    {
        "sha": "27e561ba3dc35d20f6938a32a910c8a9cd5b62c3",
        "author": "Roy Arsan",
